item.title: Someone could help me to jar my client plz? ive been trying to do it many time!
item.dc:creator: @Storm_Powner Storm Powner
item.description:
@Storm_Powner wrote:

  1. get jar maker.
  2. open it.
  3. put output directory.
  4. now back to jarmaker, at the top you see soemtinh like ####.jar, name that client.jar
  5. now click input directory and click on the folder where your .class files are and click open (btw don’t double click).
  6. know make jar.
  7. click manifest template and type client.
  8. clcik make jar and you’re done

for the rest look here: http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/tutorials/377657-pi-a7mad3absis-how-make-webclient-tutorials-images-details-p1.html
